name: Léa Elui
description:
A commission of @Alarmed_Leg_5793795.

Léa Elui is a French social media personality, with a huge fanbase in Instagram and Tiktok.

This TI has actually been sitting in my hard drive for quite a while. I created it about a month ago and didn't think it was good enough to upload to CivitAI, but, upon testing it again today, I think at the very least it's worth uploading as a 0.5 version. I may try to upgrade it in the future, though, as I think the TI would benefit from applying my most recent changes in the training process.

This was apparently just a 500-step TI, trained with my usual settings but with just 13 images in the dataset. That's what I'll probably work on during my next attempt.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
